OL,3,CWhere in the UK are you most likely to
OL,4,Cget parking fines?
OL,6,FDrivers in the South of England are
OL,7,Fmore likely to get a parking fine than
OL,8,Falmost anywhere else in the country.
OL,10,FBrighton and Hove placed at number two
OL,11,Fin a study by Claims.co.uk, analysing
OL,12,FPenalty Charge Notice data from 2020
OL,13,Fto 2021, to find the areas hardest hit
OL,14,Fwith motoring fines.
OL,16,FThe city saw fines issued at a rate of
OL,17,F98,583 per 100,000 people ` 893.62%
OL,18,Fhigher than the national average of
OL,19,F9,922 per 100,000 people.
