OL,3,CWhere in the UK are you most likely to
OL,4,Cget parking fines?
OL,6,FThroughout the timeframe, 286,280 PCNs
OL,7,Fwere issued with only 878 being
OL,8,Fappealed and 631 being successful.
OL,10,FThird on the list is Reading, with a
OL,11,FPCN issuance rate of 76,593 per
OL,12,F100,000 people.
OL,14,FReading Borough Council dealt with
OL,15,F132,636 fines during the analysed
OL,16,Fperiod relative to its population of
OL,17,F173,170 residents.
