OL,3,CWhere in the UK are you most likely to
OL,4,Cget parking fines?
OL,6,FHyndburn in Lancashire saw just 46
OL,7,Ffines issued, which works out to a
OL,8,Frate of just 56 fines per 100,000
OL,9,Fpeople - making it the UK area least
OL,10,Flikely to be hit with a PCN.
OL,12,FCarmarthenshire, Wales, had the
OL,13,Fhighest successful appeal rate of any
OL,14,FUK area.
